sentence: what is the name of the state with the lowest point ?
sentence-with-vars: what is the name of the state with the lowest point ?
sql: select highlow.state_name from highlow where highlow.lowest_elevation = ( select min ( highlow.lowest_elevation ) from highlow ) ;
